OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with showers or longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain, some heavy at times.
OL,9,FOccasionally breezy for Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with showers
OL,12,For longer spells of rain mainly for
OL,13,FOrkney, turning drier with bright
OL,14,Fspells developing later. Breezy at
OL,15,Ffirst for Orkney, easing later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
