OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,6,Fand Monday will be dry with sunny
OL,7,Fspells and variable cloud. Dry start
OL,8,Fon Tuesday with bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells, rain and freshening winds
OL,10,Fspreading northeast later.
